## 5. Prompt chain

This project uses the prompt-chain development pattern. All prompts given to Claude Code live in `./prompts/` with strict naming:

- `PROMPT-01-INIT-PROJECT.md` — first build pass (generated at scaffold time)
- `PROMPT-02-<NAME>.md` — second pass, generated via "generate next prompt" trigger
- `PROMPT-0NB-<NAME>.md` — hotfix iteration on PROMPT-0N

Rules:
- Prefix `PROMPT-`, two-digit number, letter suffix for hotfixes
- UPPERCASE hyphen-separated descriptive name
- Sequential, no gaps

